@schema_extension hive/.resource 에 per-host 4 신규 필드 추가
@field_remote_home /home/aiden | /home/summer | /root
@field_repo_path_nexus per-host nexus 트리 경로 (예: /home/aiden/Dev/nexus, /home/summer/Dev/nexus, /root/Dev/nexus)
@field_repo_path_hive per-host hive 트리 경로 (예: /home/aiden/core/hive)
@field_repo_path_hexa_lang per-host hexa-lang 트리 경로
@field_hx_packages_prefix per-host ~/.hx/packages 루트 (예: /home/aiden/.hx/packages)

@resource_lint_json_extension hive-exec resource_lint --json 가 새 4 필드 emit (remote_home, hx_packages_prefix, repo_paths{nexus,hive,hexa-lang})
@output_schema_v2 [{slug, status, description, ssh_alias, kind, capabilities, memory_gb, cpu_count, container, container_memory_cap, scoring_weight, remote_home, hx_packages_prefix, repo_paths{}}, ...]

