@added_schema_consumer RemoteHostExt {alias, prefixPerRepo from JSON, packagesPrefix from JSON}
@added_dual_rsync triggerAutoSync flatMap — 각 host 가 ~/<repo_path>/<rel> + <hx_packages_prefix>/<repo>/<rel> 둘 다 동기화. ~/.hx/packages 미러 자동 보장.

